    tutorialSteps: [
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：为什么要学不等式？\n兵力不能少于某个数——这不是等号，是不等号！\n不等式就是描述最少、最多这类限制条件的数学工具。', en: 'Zhuge Liang: Why learn inequalities?\nTroop numbers cannot fall below a certain value — that is not an equals sign, it is an inequality!\nInequalities are the maths tool for describing limits like minimum and maximum.' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：不等式和方程的区别\n方程：$3x + 5 = 20$ → 精确的一个数\n不等式：$3x + 5 > 20$ → 一个范围！\n解法一样，只是答案是范围。', en: 'Zhuge Liang: Inequality vs equation\nEquation: $3x + 5 = 20$ gives one exact number\nInequality: $3x + 5 > 20$ gives a range!\nSame method, but the answer is a range.' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：像解方程一样操作\n移项、合并同类项——和方程完全一样。', en: 'Zhuge Liang: Solve just like an equation\nRearrange terms and collect like terms — exactly the same as equations.' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：计算\n注意：乘除负数时不等号要翻转！', en: 'Zhuge Liang: Calculate\nWatch out: when multiplying or dividing by a negative number, flip the inequality sign!' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：答案\n兵力限制条件确定！', en: 'Zhuge Liang: Answer\nThe troop limit is confirmed!' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：验算\n取范围内一个值代入，应该满足不等式 ✓', en: 'Zhuge Liang: Check\nSubstitute a value within the range — it should satisfy the inequality.' }, highlightField: 'ans' },
    ],
    secret: { concept: { zh: '不等式给出范围而非单一答案。$x < 4$ 意思是 $x$ 可以是 3, 2, 1...', en: 'Inequalities give a range, not one answer. $x < 4$ means $x$ can be 3, 2, 1...' }, formula: '$ax + b < c \\Rightarrow x < \\frac{c-b}{a}$', tips: [{ zh: '诸葛亮提示：不等号像城门——有最大限度！', en: 'Zhuge Liang Tip: Inequality is like a gate — there\'s a maximum!' }] },
