    tutorialSteps: [
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：为什么情报要交叉验证？\n两条情报线索——分别给出不同的约束条件。\n只有同时满足两条线索的才是真正答案！', en: 'Zhuge Liang: "Why must intelligence be cross-checked?\nTwo intelligence leads — each gives a different constraint.\nOnly the answer that satisfies both leads is the real truth!"' }, highlightField: 'x' },
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：消元法或代入法\n选择更容易简化的方法。\n系数对称→消元法，有 $y=$ 形式→代入法。', en: 'Zhuge Liang: "Elimination or substitution\nChoose whichever simplifies more easily.\nSymmetric coefficients $\\to$ elimination, already in $y=$ form $\\to$ substitution."' }, highlightField: 'x' },
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：列方程\n线索一：$y = -x + 5$（$y$ 已经表达成关于 $x$ 的式子）\n线索二：$2x + y = 7$\n第一个方程已经是 $y=$ 形式，所以用代入法最方便！', en: 'Zhuge Liang: "Write the equations\nClue 1: $y = -x + 5$ ($y$ is already expressed in terms of $x$)\nClue 2: $2x + y = 7$\nEquation 1 is already in $y=$ form, so substitution is the best approach!"' }, highlightField: 'x' },
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：代入求解\n把 $y = -x + 5$ 代入第二个方程：\n$2x + (-x + 5) = 7$\n$x + 5 = 7$\n$x = 2$\n再回代：$y = -2 + 5 = 3$', en: 'Zhuge Liang: "Substitute and solve\nPut $y = -x + 5$ into equation 2:\n$2x + (-x + 5) = 7$\n$x + 5 = 7$\n$x = 2$\nBack-substitute: $y = -2 + 5 = 3$"' }, highlightField: 'x' },
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：答案\n$x = 2$，$y = 3$\n两条情报线索在这个点交汇——真相浮出水面！', en: 'Zhuge Liang: "Answer\n$x = 2$, $y = 3$\nBoth intelligence leads converge at this point — the truth emerges!"' }, highlightField: 'x' },
      { text: { zh: '诸葛亮：验算\n线索一：$y = -2 + 5 = 3$ ✓\n线索二：$2(2) + 3 = 7$ ✓\n两条方程都满足，情报确认！', en: 'Zhuge Liang: "Verify\nClue 1: $y = -2 + 5 = 3$ ✓\nClue 2: $2(2) + 3 = 7$ ✓\nBoth equations satisfied — intelligence confirmed!"' }, highlightField: 'x' },
    ],
