    story: { zh: '曹操将八路兵马分成三等份。$8^{1/3}$ 是多少？分数指数就像把兵力"开方"——找那个乘以自己 $n$ 次后还原的数！', en: 'Cao Cao splits eight divisions into three equal groups. What is $8^{1/3}$? Fractional indices are like "rooting" your forces — find the number that multiplied by itself $n$ times gives the original!' },
