    story: { zh: '曹操将两支 $x^3$ 部队各翻一倍再合并——$(2x^3)^2 = ax^b$。系数 $a$ 是多少？幂的幂法则：外面的指数要乘到里面的每一项！', en: 'Cao Cao doubles each of two $x^3$ divisions and merges — $(2x^3)^2 = ax^b$. What is the coefficient $a$? Power of a power rule: the outer exponent multiplies everything inside!' },
