    storyConsequence: { correct: { zh: '梯形面积精准——变速行军也难不倒你！你的图表解读能力已登堂入室。', en: 'Trapezium area spot on — even variable speed can\'t stop you! Your graph interpretation skills are masterful.' }, wrong: { zh: '梯形面积有误——记住公式：(上底+下底) $\\times$ 高 $\\div$ 2，一步一步来。', en: 'Trapezium area off — remember: (top + bottom) $\\times$ height $\\div$ 2, step by step.' } },
