    story: { zh: '斥候投掷铜板100次，正面出现53次。正面的相对频率是百分之多少？', en: 'A scout flips a coin 100 times, heads appears 53 times. What is the relative frequency of heads as a percentage?' },
    description: { zh: '100次中正面53次，相对频率=?%', en: '53 heads in 100 flips, relative frequency=?%' },
